Print the following pattern for the given N number of rows.
Pattern for N = 4
A
BC
CDE
DEFG



Solution:
import java .util.Scanner;
public class Solution {


	public static void main(String[] args) {
	Scanner s=new Scanner(System.in);
        int n=s.nextInt();
        int i=1;
		while(i<=n){
            int j=1;
            char Sc=(char)('A'+i-1);
            while(j<=i)
            {
              System.out.print(Sc);
                Sc=(char)(Sc+1);
                j++;
            }       
        System.out.println();
        i++;}
	}

}
